    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260040/extras/b72d7e384de26607bc5c40ac2106b5d9.poster.avif?t=1763621914\" width=1170 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260040/extras/b72d7e384de26607bc5c40ac2106b5d9.webm?t=1763621914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260040/extras/b72d7e384de26607bc5c40ac2106b5d9.mp4?t=1763621914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能探索多深？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《寒冷深渊》是一款轻松惬意的沉浸式探索游戏，故事发生在空寂深邃的海底。你的目标十分简单：修复毁坏的电缆。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《寒冷深渊：导演剪辑版》将呈现新的游戏关卡、额外故事剧情，以及重制的移动操作系统。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不论是寻找宁静，还是另有所求—— </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >广袤的大海无疑是放松身心的理想之地。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260040/extras/7d184472ad0614e93e755d08662c0d35.poster.avif?t=1763621914\" width=1170 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260040/extras/7d184472ad0614e93e755d08662c0d35.webm?t=1763621914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260040/extras/7d184472ad0614e93e755d08662c0d35.mp4?t=1763621914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜入海底，感受别致的寂静。 </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富原版《寒冷深渊》游戏内容，新增关卡与剧情。 </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >画面与玩法优化升级。 </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集文物，探索更多乐趣。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260040/extras/63819935db58730dd20a70c14e5ec1f3.poster.avif?t=1763621914\" width=1170 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260040/extras/63819935db58730dd20a70c14e5ec1f3.webm?t=1763621914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260040/extras/63819935db58730dd20a70c14e5ec1f3.mp4?t=1763621914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
